data-triple-N3.o: "Sort is the capital of the comarca of Pallars Sobira, in the province of Lleida, Catalonia, in the country of Spain. It is located at 692metres above the sea, by the river Noguera Pallaresa, a tributary to the Segre. Population 2,113 (2005). It was once capital of the County of Pallars. The word sort is Catalan for "luck"."@en
